These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, documentary
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | documentary |
| Transport     | scooter | jet-ski  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: banana, avocado
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, swimming
1. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | banana      | avocado         |
| Sport   | lacrosse | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, mango
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | water   |
| Food       | mango  | cauliflower |

 #################################

 
